{
  "stem": "268.9",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have seen acts of courage like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have seen acts of courage of believing-- religious-- religious acts of courage, such as-- I remember in this one camp-- in Dyhernfurth, as a matter of fact, at night, I would wake up, and the guy below me, his bunk was empty.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I looked down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He must have went to the toilet outside, outside toilet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But time goes by, he's not back-- half an hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, where could he be?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I began to get worried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Surely, he didn't grab the wire, because sometimes, they would go out and grab the wire and commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I would look around, get up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I finally found him at the end of the-- of the barrack-- of the room, between two other berths.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I see this figure-- what am I trying to say-- rocking back and forth in a standing position.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was paying at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He got up-- somehow, he got a little prayer book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know how he smuggled it in-- a small, little prayer book.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was flicking pages and praying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I certainly thought that was a courageous act, because if they would catch him praying or his prayer book, they would kill him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when they were distributing food, in the soup, sometimes, you would find a piece of meat swimming, which would be a piece of bacon, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would find one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He would shove it aside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A starving inmate would push it aside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He's not going to touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he wouldn't let another Jewish guy touch it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But he would talk to, say, a Russian inmate or Ukranian or what have you, and would say, would you like this soup?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I will trade you for two potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
